Date: 1998-10-02

Title: Four-dimensional QCD and fiberwise duality

Comments: Paper as published in JHEP011999005, new references on duality added,

misprint corrected, minor changesJournal-ref: JHEP 9901 (1999) 005

We transform, by means of a fiberwise duality, the partition function of QCDon a product of two two-tori, into a four-dimensional sigma-model, whose targetspace is the cotangent space of unitary connections on the fiber torusfiberwise.